    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "small moments aren't helping. it just feels like i'm running in place. like i'm just waiting for the next thing to break or the next thing to leave. i'm just so tired of fighting to make everything okay when nothing actually is. i just want the noise in my head to stop. i want it to be quiet for real.",
