      "content": "but \"letting go\" of the noise... it feels like it would require so much more energy than i have left. i'm just so done with the struggle. it feels like there's no actual way to get that real quietness without just... giving up on everything. like there's no point in even trying to heal when the end result is always just more emptiness.",
